{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-jsx","path":"/Neovim/16-floaterm/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"2fff9985-80ed-591d-8887-fc3cde33aded","html":"<h2>Install</h2>\n<code-fence lang=\"null\" null>\n    <textarea vue-slot=\"code\">\n      Plug 'voldikss/vim-floaterm'\n    </textarea>\n    </code-fence>\n  \n<h2>Create config file</h2>\n<code-fence lang=\"null\" null>\n    <textarea vue-slot=\"code\">\n      touch ~/.config/nvim/plug-config/floaterm.vim\n    </textarea>\n    </code-fence>\n  \n<p>Make sure to source this file in <code class=\"language-text\">init.vim</code></p>\n<code-fence lang=\"null\" null>\n    <textarea vue-slot=\"code\">\n      source $HOME/.config/nvim/plug-config/floaterm.vim\n    </textarea>\n    </code-fence>\n  \n<h2>Floaterm</h2>\n<p>Floaterm is a floating terminal for Neovim</p>\n<h3>Configure Floaterm</h3>\n<code-fence lang=\"null\" null>\n    <textarea vue-slot=\"code\">\n      let g:floaterm_keymap_toggle = '<F1>'\nlet g:floaterm_keymap_next   = '<F2>'\nlet g:floaterm_keymap_prev   = '<F3>'\nlet g:floaterm_keymap_new    = '<F4>'\n\n\" Floaterm\nlet g:floaterm_gitcommit='floaterm'\nlet g:floaterm_autoinsert=1\nlet g:floaterm_width=0.8\nlet g:floaterm_height=0.8\nlet g:floaterm_wintitle=0\nlet g:floaterm_autoclose=1\n    </textarea>\n    </code-fence>\n  \n<h3>Floaterm Commands</h3>\n<p>Here is my which key configuration:</p>\n<code-fence lang=\"null\" null>\n    <textarea vue-slot=\"code\">\n      let g:which_key_map.t = {\n      \\ 'name' : '+terminal' ,\n      \\ ';' : [':FloatermNew --wintype=popup --height=6'        , 'terminal'],\n      \\ 'f' : [':FloatermNew fzf'                               , 'fzf'],\n      \\ 'g' : [':FloatermNew lazygit'                           , 'git'],\n      \\ 'd' : [':FloatermNew lazydocker'                        , 'docker'],\n      \\ 'n' : [':FloatermNew node'                              , 'node'],\n      \\ 'N' : [':FloatermNew nnn'                               , 'nnn'],\n      \\ 'p' : [':FloatermNew python'                            , 'python'],\n      \\ 'r' : [':FloatermNew ranger'                            , 'ranger'],\n      \\ 't' : [':FloatermToggle'                                , 'toggle'],\n      \\ 'y' : [':FloatermNew ytop'                              , 'ytop'],\n      \\ 's' : [':FloatermNew ncdu'                              , 'ncdu'],\n      \\ }\n    </textarea>\n    </code-fence>\n  \n<h2>Link to Floaterm repo</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/voldikss/vim-floaterm\">Floaterm</a></p>","excerpt":"Install Create config file Make sure to source this file in  Floaterm Floaterm is a floating terminal for Neovim Configure Floaterm Floatermâ€¦","frontmatter":{"title":"Floaterm","tags":["neovim"],"image":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/ff1c356d6a7f46604822f50919abcf83/a8734/neovim.png"},"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":3.456140350877193,"src":"/static/ff1c356d6a7f46604822f50919abcf83/5134e/neovim.png","srcSet":"/static/ff1c356d6a7f46604822f50919abcf83/06f82/neovim.png 197w,\n/static/ff1c356d6a7f46604822f50919abcf83/da7d7/neovim.png 393w,\n/static/ff1c356d6a7f46604822f50919abcf83/5134e/neovim.png 786w,\n/static/ff1c356d6a7f46604822f50919abcf83/31987/neovim.png 1000w","sizes":"(max-width: 786px) 100vw, 786px"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/Neovim/16-floaterm/","prev":{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/Linux/04-i3wm/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Configuring i3wm","tags":["archlinux"]}}},"next":{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/Linux/03-AUR-yay/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Install packages from AUR with yay","tags":["archlinux"]}}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3649515864"]}